00:00:16.070 --> 00:00:19.620
That looks more like green
water, but I think you get

00:00:19.620 --> 00:00:20.500
what I'm saying.

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:23.150
So I throw a ball at a 45 degree
angle and I throw it

00:00:23.150 --> 00:00:24.940
at-- what did I say?

00:00:24.940 --> 00:00:26.930
I think it was 10 meters
per second.

00:00:30.210 --> 00:00:33.710
I want to figure out how far
this ball will go or how high

00:00:33.710 --> 00:00:34.910
does-- not how high.

00:00:34.910 --> 00:00:36.220
Well, I could figure
that out as well.

00:00:36.220 --> 00:00:38.480
Or how long does the ball
