00:00:38.480 --> 00:00:41.820
And what we said is we can
break this vector.

00:00:41.820 --> 00:00:46.610
This vector has magnitude 10
in the 45 degree direction.

00:00:46.610 --> 00:00:51.030
We can break into its vertical
and horizontal components.

00:00:51.030 --> 00:00:54.600
So it's horizontal components,
this horizontal component

00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:56.330
